entry.title: Ukraine Counterattack Takes Back Parts of Strategic Donbas City
entry.content: Close urban combat in Severodonetsk makes it harder for Russia to use artillery, as Kyiv awaits the arrival of a long-range rocket system from the U.S.

entry.title: Hong Kong Police Quash Vigil to Mark Tiananmen Square Massacre
entry.content: Hong Kong police blanketed a busy district and stopped people entering a park that traditionally held a mass vigil on the anniversary of the Tiananmen Square Massacre, but many people staged small acts of defiance.
